    "The use of different International System of Units (SI) units alone presents a common nontrivial challenge.",
    "Only when a high standard is established during data collection can general concepts such as the FAIR principles 5 be effectively implemented.",
    "31 Our SQLite-based database solution uniquely addresses the challenges of clinical RDM by integrating user needs, technical requirements, and industry standards.",
    "It prioritizes clear storage structure, ease of access, data security, and rights management, ensuring an uncomplicated and efficient RDM process.",
